o de polvo de sílice\\Nrespirable en vías aéreas distales","guid":"0Fm8vyja0sZYEYZyvmjSFA","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"- Macrófagos alveolares\\Ninteractúan e ingieren partículas\\Nde sílice --> inflamación","guid":"3LNaXFw-aXig7vYFUM5NQA","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"- Inflamación ---> fibrosis y formación\\Nde nódulos silicóticos con colágeno en\\Nlóbulos superiores (5)","guid":"PQaE495fg0KLydq9E-SWHQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"0","text":"Historia y\\Nexploración\\Nfísica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"4.1\\NPresentación\\Nclínica:","guid":"H0PJ3gE_T5xgT3JG3E7jxQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Tabla 1 (2):","guid":"ZGGdeddZlSxmON4pYIPZ3g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"0","text":"4.2 Historia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"4.2.1 Motivo consulta: Insuficiencia\\Nrespiratoria si es grave (1,2)","guid":"6R-7SeYkPyisOOjYgdA7Kw","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"4.2.2 Enfermedad actual:\\NSíntomas pueden tardar\\Naños en aparecer (2)","guid":"Zok0zp-B_A6F4-VKrcKrHA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"4.2.3 Antec. médicos: Preguntar por\\Ncondiciones asociadas (1)","guid":"PpR8wgx-XSf4nDTwhfAeMQ","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"4.2.4 Hª social: Ocupaciones/industrias\\Ncon exposición a sílice (1,2)","guid":"xghJqOccl9JT09gkkloEbQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"4.3 Explor. física:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"4.3.1 General: Valorar\\Nsignos constitucionales\\N(fiebre, pérdida peso) (1)","guid":"pF5SLgtxUYfSeZYCA35AzQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"4.3.2 Piel: Telangiectasias,\\Nengrosamiento si esclerosis sistémica\\N(1)","guid":"Nqnda1PXH0K4ZapoG8o2Pg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"4.3.3 Cardiovascular:\\NHipertensión pulmonar sugiere\\Nenfermedad avanzada (6)","guid":"Wmimnpz_7o4aOUINyO-tCA","children":[]},{"id":"61","pa